{"tid":882931,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌","createTime":"2018-10-30T12:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T13:43:32.000Z","uid":31254,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7290349547eabd5920cf846c2edb0117643cb7","tid":882931,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 恆生管理學院BBA進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n<br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"d72bfa3c85030631c8b6d658804b31e4ea4476fe","tid":882931,"uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6i2nnOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6i2nnOc.png&h=5e1add68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5484df1d22c471c314d031b084966a2e50f55aa1","tid":882931,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72bfa3c85030631c8b6d658804b31e4ea4476fe","tid":882931,"uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6i2nnOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6i2nnOc.png&h=5e1add68&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"貼我做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ec8793981fdd261581fa4e4ea4652cf4ce9dc6","tid":882931,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5484df1d22c471c314d031b084966a2e50f55aa1","tid":882931,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72bfa3c85030631c8b6d658804b31e4ea4476fe","tid":882931,"uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6i2nnOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6i2nnOc.png&h=5e1add68&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"貼我做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/O8XKQpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO8XKQpP.png&h=98a35a4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a03835d9e94dda7bc6f42944cb90bbe4f024e74","tid":882931,"uid":152520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:52:43.000Z","msg":"恒咩管理大學啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱出嚟？"},{"pid":"44382b8b3a4d1e8916417ceef048d566bf8a924a","tid":882931,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"恆大仔一到店，所有便利店員便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「含大仔，你臉上又添上新的梅毒瘤了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「要盒幼卡碧，要一盒杜蕾斯。」便排出中銀恆大信用卡。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又偷拍人家裙底拿去賣錢了！」恆大仔睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你偷拍林鄭葉私煙劉裙底，一邊打J。」恆大仔便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「竊春光不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊春光！&hellip;&hellip;大學生的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「香港一大」，什麼「升格」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"}]}